Project: Platformer 4
Student: Logan Barnes (ltbarnes)

Hovercraft racing game. Race through the cyan colored waypoints and don't get knocked of the edge! Press 'G' to toggle GRAPHICS CARD DESTRUCTION MODE!!! dun dun dun... (no 2D ortho projections in this mode)


Controls:

	  W 			- 		move forward
	 A/D			-		turn left/right

	  8				- 		toggle camera lock
	  						(locks camera behind player)

	 +/- 			-  		change camera zoom
	mouse			- 		move camera (when unlocked)

  Backspace 		- 		back to menu

